# Data & Storage

Implement only per approved spec. ADRs: 002, 005.

## Paths

- User data: `~/.personal_dev_tracker/data.json` (Phase 1 daily entries)
- Future fitness: `~/.personal_dev_tracker/fitness.db` (SQLite)
- Progress photos: `~/.personal_dev_tracker/photos/`

## Daily Entry Shape

```json
{
  "rating": 7,
  "checklist": { "item": true },
  "metrics": { "Sleep hours last night": 7.5 },
  "notes": "journal text"
}
```

Dates as `YYYY-MM-DD` keys. Categories match the 8 default domains in `docs/DATA_MODEL.md`.

## Conventions

- All file I/O through a `storage` module — UI never opens files directly.
- `save_data()` writes atomically (write temp → rename) when file grows large.
- UTF-8 encoding, `ensure_ascii=False` for notes/journal.
- Streaks: consecutive calendar days with logs ending today; category-scoped variant per card.

## 8 Categories

Money/Freedom, Body & Presence, Burnout Prevention & Energy Management, Creative/Mental Work, Family/Logistics, Search Practice, Spiritual Development, Emotional Wellbeing.

Do not rename categories without migration — breaks historical entries.
